# UniGo "Never-Falls-Over" Pack (ORIGINAL, principles inspired by super-apps)

Generated: 2026-03-02T15:23:26.203465Z

This pack extends the earlier principles pack with reliability layers:

- Idempotency keys (no duplicate orders/payments)
- DB-backed job queue + worker endpoint (async push/dispatch/billing)
- DB-backed rate limiting (anti-abuse)
- Double-entry payments ledger foundation
- Health endpoint + structured logging

This is NOT copied from any third-party app.